name: Avocado Toast
description: Sourdough toast topped with creamy avocado slices, drizzled with olive oil, and seasoned with salt and pepper. A nutritious and delicious choice.

name: Espresso
description: A bold and flavorful shot of espresso, meticulously brewed to showcase the distinctive characteristics of the coffee beans.

name: Bagel with Lox
description: A classic New York bagel topped with cream cheese, smoked salmon (lox), red onion, and capers. A savory and satisfying breakfast option.

name: Almond Croissant
description: A delightful twist on the classic croissant, filled with almond paste and topped with sliced almonds. A sweet and nutty treat.

name: Croissant
description: A buttery and flaky croissant, baked to golden perfection. Ideal for pairing with your morning coffee.

name: Americano
description: A bold and invigorating coffee drink made by diluting a shot of espresso with hot water, offering a robust flavor with a smooth finish.

name: Spinach and Feta Croissant
description: A savory croissant filled with spinach and feta cheese. Perfect for a quick and satisfying snack.

name: Ham and Cheese Croissant
description: A classic croissant filled with ham and melted cheese. A hearty and delicious breakfast option.

name: Latte
description: A smooth and satisfying blend of espresso and steamed milk, finished with a touch of foam. Ideal for those seeking a comforting coffee experience.

name: Turkey and Avocado Sandwich
description: A fresh and tasty sandwich made with sliced turkey, creamy avocado, lettuce, and tomato, served on whole grain bread.

name: Chicken Caesar Salad
description: A classic Caesar salad topped with grilled chicken, crisp romaine lettuce, Parmesan cheese, and croutons, drizzled with Caesar dressing.

name: Fruit Parfait
description: A refreshing and healthy parfait made with layers of yogurt, fresh fruit, and granola. Perfect for breakfast or a light snack.

name: Affogato
description: A delightful dessert made by pouring a shot of hot espresso over a scoop of vanilla gelato, creating a perfect blend of hot and cold.

name: Mocha
description: An indulgent blend of espresso, steamed milk, and chocolate syrup, topped with whipped cream. A delightful treat for chocolate and coffee enthusiasts.

name: Caramel Macchiato
description: A decadent espresso-based drink with steamed milk and caramel syrup, finished with a drizzle of caramel sauce.

name: Hazelnut Latte
description: A rich latte flavored with hazelnut syrup, topped with whipped cream and a sprinkle of hazelnut crumbles.

name: Iced Americano
description: A refreshing iced coffee made by diluting espresso with cold water, served over ice for a cool and bold flavor.

name: Turmeric Latte
description: A warm and soothing latte made with steamed milk, turmeric, and a hint of honey. Known for its health benefits and vibrant color.

name: Iced Latte
description: A chilled coffee beverage made with espresso, cold milk, and ice. Perfect for enjoying on a warm day.

name: Flat White
description: A creamy and balanced coffee drink made with a shot of espresso and velvety steamed milk, topped with a delicate layer of microfoam.

name: Cappuccino
description: A classic cappuccino crafted with equal parts espresso, steamed milk, and frothy milk foam. Rich and creamy with a balanced flavor profile.

name: Blueberry Muffin
description: A freshly baked muffin bursting with juicy blueberries. Ideal for a quick breakfast or snack.

name: Pumpkin Spice Latte
description: A seasonal latte made with espresso, steamed milk, pumpkin pie spice, and a hint of vanilla, topped with whipped cream and cinnamon.

name: Maple Pecan Latte
description: A seasonal favorite latte infused with maple syrup and topped with a sprinkle of toasted pecans, capturing the essence of autumn.

name: Tiramisu
description: A classic Italian dessert served in a coffee shop, featuring layers of coffee-soaked ladyfingers, mascarpone cheese, and cocoa powder.

name: Chai Latte
description: A soothing spiced tea latte made with black tea, steamed milk, and aromatic spices like cinnamon, cardamom, and cloves.

name: Espresso Martini
description: A sophisticated cocktail made with vodka, coffee liqueur, and a shot of espresso, shaken with ice and strained into a martini glass.

name: Orange Mocha
description: A unique twist on the classic mocha, infused with fresh orange zest and topped with a slice of orange, offering a refreshing citrus flavor.

name: Coconut Milk Mocha
description: A creamy mocha made with espresso, steamed coconut milk, and chocolate syrup, finished with whipped cream and coconut flakes.

name: Quiche Lorraine
description: A savory quiche filled with bacon, Swiss cheese, and onions, baked to perfection in a buttery crust.

name: Veggie Wrap
description: A nutritious wrap filled with grilled vegetables, hummus, spinach, and feta cheese, wrapped in a whole wheat tortilla.

name: Chocolate Chip Cookie
description: A freshly baked chocolate chip cookie, soft and chewy with chunks of premium chocolate throughout.

name: Cold Brew
description: A refreshing and smooth coffee drink brewed by steeping coarse coffee grounds in cold water for an extended period. Rich in flavor and low in acidity.

description: A toasted bagel topped with cream cheese, smoked salmon, capers, red onion, and fresh dill, offering a savory and satisfying breakfast option.
